OL,3,CDoncaster man campaigning for glass
OL,4,Cban after being blinded on night out
OL,6,FA man from Doncaster is backing a
OL,7,Fcampaign for a glass ban in pubs after
OL,8,F9pm after he was left blind in one eye
OL,9,Fwhen a stranger smashed a pint glass
OL,10,Fin his face.
OL,12,FAdam Lowe, age 30, was attacked by a
OL,13,Fstranger in July whilst out on a night
OL,14,Fout in Doncaster leaving him with
OL,15,Ffacial scarring and total blindness in
OL,16,Fhis right eye.
