OL,3,CDoncaster man campaigning for glass
OL,4,Cban after being blinded on night out
OL,6,FAdam, who had been body building for
OL,7,Fthree years, had bumped into a friend
OL,8,Fat the gym in the morning who had
OL,9,Fsuggested going for drinks in
OL,10,FDoncaster later that day. He told ITV
OL,11,FNews that as he was having drinks at
OL,12,Fthe Courtyard Pub in Doncaster an
OL,13,Funknown man had a problem with him
OL,14,Ffrom the go, making comments about
OL,15,FAdam's size.
OL,17,FAdam said he told him that he "wasn't
OL,18,Fthere for trouble" before heading to
OL,19,Fthe bar to get a drink.
