OL,3,CDoncaster man campaigning for glass
OL,4,Cban after being blinded on night out
OL,6,F"The next thing I know I just got
OL,7,Fglassed."
OL,9,FThe attack lasted just seconds but has
OL,10,Fhad lasting impacts on Adam's life,
OL,11,Fcausing him to be completely blind in
OL,12,Fhis right eye.
OL,14,FHe added: 'I woke up and was about to
OL,15,Fgo into theatre and I grabbed the
OL,16,Fsurgeon's arm and said I can't see, I
OL,17,Fcan't see. I then had a six hour
OL,18,Foperation on my eyeball.
