OL,3,CDoncaster man campaigning for glass
OL,4,Cban after being blinded on night out
OL,6,F"The doctor sat me down and said
OL,7,Fyou're never going to get your sight
OL,8,Fback."
OL,10,FAdam still has glass in his eye four
OL,11,Fmonths on and is unable to go to the
OL,12,Fgym, an activity he used to do most
OL,13,Fdays.
OL,15,FDespite his injuries, the underground
OL,16,Fcable joiner says becoming a father
OL,17,Feight weeks ago has given him a new
OL,18,Fperspective.
