OL,4,Cban after being blinded on night out
OL,6,FHe added: "Could I imagine if I didn't
OL,7,Fhave my eyesight to watch my son be
OL,8,Fborn or grow up. I'm very grateful to
OL,9,Fhave this one eye to see him grow up.''
OL,11,FAdam is now backing a campaign calling
OL,12,Ffor all pubs and clubs to use only
OL,13,Fplastic cups after 9pm.
OL,15,FThe campaign was launched by Matthew
OL,16,FSyron who was hit in the face with a
OL,17,Fglass bottle in Leeds and blinded.
