OL,6,FMr Syron, who lives in Australia with
OL,7,Fhis fiancee and two children, has been
OL,8,Fvisiting family in his home city when
OL,9,Fthe attack happened on Boxing Day last
OL,10,Fyear.
OL,12,FHis attacker, 37-year-old Gareth Dean,
OL,13,Fwas jailed for ten years in March for
OL,14,Fthe unprovoked attack.
OL,16,FSpeaking about his decision to back
OL,17,FMatthews petition, Adam said: "It's
OL,18,Fjust so easy for someone to pick that
OL,19,Fweapon up and do that without even
OL,20,Frealising what it could do to someone."
